    • Method Detail

      • resolve

        public com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode resolve(URI uri)
        Resolve a given URI to read its contents and parse the result as JSON.

        Supported protocols:

        • http/https
        • file
        • classpath/resource/java (all synonymous, used to resolve a schema from the classpath)
        Parameters:
        uri - the URI to read schema content from
        Returns:
        the JSON tree found at the given URI
